data.description: Don't Miss This Unbelievable Opportunity!!!HUGE PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!! Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought after Felida Neighborhood! This custom-built 5-bedroom, 3.1-bathroom masterpiece boasts luxury and functionality in every corner. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the attention to detail and the numerous upgrades including granite and quartz countertops, custom cabinetry, and a gourmet kitchen with an industrial cooktop ventilation system. The primary suite is a true sanctuary, complete with a double vanity, jetted tub, a tile walk-in shower, and a custom-built walk-in closet, offering both luxury and practicality. This home has been thoughtfully designed for multi-generational living or hosting guests with the 2-bedroom guest quarters on the main level, featuring an ADA bathroom for accessibility. Outdoor living is equally impressive, with professionally landscaped front and back yards that include a fire pit area, expansive covered outdoor living space and a hot tub. One unique feature of this property is the separate entrance to an oversize 6-foot crawl space, which could be transformed into an exceptional wine cellar for wine connoisseurs. Additionally, this property includes a 24x40 ft. shop with a 16ft door in the front and an 8ft door to the yard, providing ample space for your projects and storage needs. There's also a 12x40 RV cover, ensuring your recreational vehicles are well-protected. This is not just a beautiful home; it's also a green energy marvel, boasting a 95% energy efficiency rating. Don't miss your opportunity to own this exceptional custom-built home.
